CONFIG FILE FOR QIIME2_HPC

----------Filepaths---------------------------------------------------------------

.fastq files: /cm/shared/courses/gauthier/Microbiome/

metadata files: /cm/shared/courses/gauthier/Microbiome/

__________________________________________________________________________________

----------Script 3: preprocessing-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
275		qiime dada2 denoise-paired --p-trunc-len-f <integer>				Right-trim forward sequences
275             qiime dada2 denoise-paired --p-trunc-len-r <integer>           			Right-trim reverse sequences
17		qiime dada2 denoise-paired --trim-len-f <integer>				Left-trim (primer) forward sequences
21              qiime dada2 denoise-paired --trim-len-r <integer>              			Left-trim (primer) reverse sequences
2		qiime dada2 denoise-paired --p-min-fold-parent-over-abundance <integer>		Set fold-overabundance for chimera detection
50		qiime diversity alpha-rarefaction --p-steps <integer>				# of sampling steps between min and max depth (below)
1000		qiime diversity alpha-rarefaction --p-min-depth	<integer>			minimum sampling depth for alpha rarefaction
50000		qiime diversity alpha-rarefaction --p-max-depth <integer>			maximum sampling depth for alpha rarefaction
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

----------Script 4: filter and run core metrics-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
10000           	qiime feature-table filter-samples --p-min-frequency <integer>			Minimum coverage cutoff.  Determine from alpha-rarefaction.
allassigned		FILTTAX filename variable <string>						Descriptive string for taxonomy filtration
nocontrol_wild_noSI	FILTMETA filename variable <string>						Descriptive string for metadata filtration

exclude "unassigned"	taxonomy filtration argument 1 <exclude/include> <"string">
mode "exact"		taxonomy filtration argument 1 <exact/contains> <"string">

exclude "d__Bacteria"	taxonomy filtration argument 2 <exclude/include> <"string">
mode "exact"		taxonomy filtration argument 2 <exact/contains> <"string">

exclude "chloroplast"	taxonomy filtration argument 3 <exclude/include> <"string">
mode "contains"		taxonomy filtration argument 3 <exact/contains> <"string">

where "[Biome] LIKE 'wild caught%' AND NOT [Location] = 'SI'"	metadata filtration argument 1  <mySQL where statement>
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


----------Script 5: filter and run core metrics-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
shannon			alpha diversity metric <string>
bray_curtis		beta diversity metric <string>
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


----------Script 6: alpha and univariate beta diversity stats---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Rp_status		comparison variable for univariate beta diversity comparison <string>		Must match metadata heading
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

----------Script 7: multivariate beta diversity stats-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Location*Rp_status	qiime diversity adonis --p-formula <string>					Use var1+var2 for confounders, var1*var2 for crossed terms
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

----------Script 8: ANCOM---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------      
5			qiime taxa collapse --p-level <integer>			1-Kingdom, 2-Phylum, 3-Class, 4-Order, 5-Family, 6-Genus, 7-Species (no collapse)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
